nt%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F04141303%2FFjHNMmeakAEkbxa.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20addressed%20the%20Haryana%20communal%20violence%20and%20its%20relation%20to%20the%20upcoming%20G20%20summit%20at%20a%20press%20briefing%20on%20Thursday%2C%20August%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBagchi%20was%20answering%20a%20question%20by%20%3Cem%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98s%20Shudhir%20Ranjan%20about%20whether%20the%20MEA%20was%20concerned%20by%20the%20violence%20taking%20place%20a%20few%20weeks%20away%20from%20the%20G20%20summit%2C%20and%20if%20it%20was%20in%20touch%20with%20other%20Union%20ministries%20about%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLook%2C%20of%20course%2C%20we%20would%20like%20to%20see%20a%20return%20to%20normalcy%20and%20peace%2C%20but%20this%20is%20an%20area%20that%20our%20other%20ministers%20%E2%80%A6%20I%20mean%2C%20it%20is%20not%20a%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20issue%2C%20and%20I%20am%20sure%20our%20local%20authorities%20as%20well%20as%20other%20agencies%20are%20working%20on%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bagchi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fmedia-briefings.htm%3Fdtl%2F36961%2FTranscript%2Bof%2BWeekly%2BMedia%2BBriefing%2Bby%2Bthe%2BOfficial%2BSpokesperson%2BAugust%2B03%2B2023%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ranjan%20further%20asked%20if%20the%20MEA%20was%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20home%20ministry%2C%20Bagchi%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20need%20to%20discuss%20with%20them%20to%20ensure%20peace%20and%20normalcy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20we%20would%20hopefully%20see%20a%20very%20successful%20G20%20summit%20next%20month%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViolence%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20in%20Haryana%20erupted%20on%20Monday%2C%20July%2031%2C%20after%20a%20clash%20at%20a%20Hindu%20religious%20procession%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Nuh%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20spread%20to%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20state%2C%20including%20to%20Gurugram%20(formerly%20Gurgaon)%20district%2C%20the%20headquarters%20of%20which%20houses%20the%20offices%20of%20many%20multinational%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20agency%20Reuters%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Fhindu-muslim-riots-expose-risk-major-indian-business-hub-2023-08-03%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20violence%20disrupted%20everyday%20life%20in%20the%20area%20by%20prompting%20school%20closures%20and%20work-from-home%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20has%20seen%20seven%20people%20lose%20their%20lives%20and%20a%20mobile%20internet%20ban%20imposed%20on%20three%20of%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20districts%2C%20which%20are%20together%20home%20to%20over%20thirty%20lakh%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharyana-violence-mewat-hate-and-provocative-videos%5C%22%3EHow%20Provocative%20Videos%20and%20a%20Background%20of%20Hate%20Preceded%20the%20Nuh%20Riots%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MEA%20is%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20nodal%20agency%20for%20organising%20the%20G20%20summit%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20like%20Bagchi%20said%2C%20local%20authorities%20in%20Delhi%20are%20also%20closely%20involved%20in%20preparing%20the%20city%20for%20the%20summit%E2%80%99s%20main%20events%20in%20early%20September%2C%20which%20will%20see%20world%20leaders%20such%20as%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20and%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20in%20attendance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fdelhi-news%2Fmcd-to-remove-street-dogs-in-delhi-from-g20-sites-101691086416765.html%5C%22%3Ea%20report%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20newspaper%2C%20preparations%20are%20in%20place%20to%20relocate%20many%20of%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20stray%20dogs%20%E2%80%93%20which%20are%20estimated%20to%20number%20over%20eight%20lakh%20in%20total%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20upcoming%20weeks%20from%20areas%20likely%20to%20receive%20G20%20delegates%20and%20tourists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20that%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20(MCD)%20began%20relocating%20dogs%20to%20animal%20birth%20control%20(ABC)%20centres%20starting%20on%20Friday%2C%20August%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAreas%20so%20far%20identified%20for%20the%20relocation%20drive%20include%20historic%20sites%20such%20as%20the%20Red%20Fort%20and%20Jama%20Masjid%2C%20and%20upmarket%20localities%20such%20as%20Hauz%20Khas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20paper%2C%20the%20MCD%E2%80%99s%20veterinary%20department%20plans%20to%20relocate%20dogs%20to%20ABC%20centres%20for%20up%20to%20six%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20animal%20rights%20activist%20Ambika%20Shukla%20said%20that%20this%20would%20contravene%20the%20Animal%20Birth%20Control%20Rules%2C%202023%2C%20which%20says%20that%20dogs%20may%20he%20housed%20in%20ABCs%20for%20a%20maximum%20of%20just%20seven%20days%2C%20unless%20they%20are%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLifting%20dogs%20at%20such%20a%20large-scale%20is%20unheard%20of.%20Our%20ABC%20centres%20are%20already%20operating%20at%20their%20maximum%20capacity%20and%20some%20of%20these%20centres%20only%20have%20a%20holding%20capacity%20of%20around%2040%20dogs%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20her%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20will%20they%20fall%20sick%2C%20but%20the%20rules%20state%20a%20dog%20can%20only%20be%20kept%20for%20a%20maximum%20period%20of%20seven%20days%2C%20unless%20there%20is%20a%20wound.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDelhi%20has%20hosted%20several%20such%20world%20events%20in%20the%20past%2C%2