0outdated.%3Cp%3EJennifer%20Ortakales%20Dawkins%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EI%20visited%20the%20Macy's%20flagship%20store%20in%20New%20York%20City%20and%20tried%20on%20its%20new%20%26quot%3BOn%2034th%26quot%3B%20private%20label.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMost%20of%20the%20styles%20were%20lackluster%20and%20outdated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20store%20appeared%20to%20be%20severely%20understaffed%20%E2%80%94%20no%20one%20helped%20me%20get%20a%20dressing%20room%20or%20at%20the%20register.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20summer%2C%20Macy's%20is%20launching%20On%2034th%2C%20a%20women's%20brand%20promising%20to%20solve%20common%20fit%20issues%20and%20provide%20styles%20that%20can%20be%20mixed%20and%20matched.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20this%20would%20be%20a%20good%20opportunity%20to%20check%20out%20the%20new%20line%20and%20experience%20shopping%20at%20the%20iconic%20retailer%20%E2%80%93%20as%20a%20millennial%20who%20admittedly%20doesn't%20frequent%20department%20stores%20very%20often.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20to%20Macy's%20famous%20flagship%20store%20on%2034th%20Street%20in%20Manhattan%2C%20and%20while%20it%20had%20plenty%20of%20selection%2C%20it%20failed%20to%20capture%20my%20interest%20with%20its%20lackluster%20displays%20and%20elusive%20staff.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMacy's%20revenues%20fell%20about%207%25%20year-over-year%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%2C%20to%20%244.98%20billion%2C%20and%20a%20recent%20UBS%20report%20expects%20Macy's%20to%20continue%20to%20lose%20customers%20as%20shoppers%20gravitate%20to%20online%20channels%20and%20off-price%20retailers%20like%20TJ%20Maxx.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMacy's%20has%20a%20real%20problem%20with%20merchandising%2C%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20buying%20product%2C%20allocating%20product%2C%20and%20displaying%20product%20in%20a%20compelling%20way%20in%20its%20stores%2C%26quot%3B%20retail%20analyst%20Neil%20Saunders%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20end%20result%20is%20a%20very%20disjointed%20offer%20that%20does%20not%20come%20across%20clearly%20to%20the%20consumer%20and%20isn't%20all%20that%20targeted%20at%20any%20particular%20type%20of%20consumer.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaunders%20told%20Insider%20he's%20visited%20more%20than%2050%20Macy's%20stores%20across%20the%20country%20this%20year.%20%26quot%3BThe%20one%20thing%20that%20they%20all%20have%20in%20common%20is%20that%20they're%20abysmal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BMacy's%20is%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20retailers%20for%20shopkeeping%20standards%20in%20the%20country.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20witnessed%20some%20of%20this%20disarray%20during%20my%20visit.%20A%20highly%20stylized%20Ralph%20Lauren%20Polo%20shop%20was%20a%20bright%20spot%20in%20an%20otherwise%20faltering%20store.%20%C2%A0Table%20displays%20were%20either%20sparse%20or%20cluttered%2C%20the%20mannequins%20were%20dressed%20in%20dull%20and%20frumpy%20outfits%2C%20and%20finding%20a%20store%20employee%20was%20a%20game%20of%20%26quot%3BWhere's%20Waldo.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Macy's%20spokesperson%20provided%20the%20following%20comment%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20invite%20our%20customers%20to%20own%20their%20style%20and%20provide%20merchandise%20and%20displays%20that%20showcase%20product%20versatility%20and%20different%20styling%20options%20to%20inspire%20them.%20With%20ebbs%20in%20customer%20traffic%20and%20the%20current%20transition%20of%20seasonal%20merchandise%2C%20there%20may%20be%20times%20when%20some%20areas%20of%20the%20store%20are%20not%20in%20keeping%20with%20our%20standards.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20stopped%20by%20Macy's%20iconic%20flagship%20store%20in%20Herald%20Square%20on%20a%20Tuesday%2C%20late%20in%20the%20afternoon.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224436%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sign%20that%20marks%20the%20Macy's%20store%20is%20seen%20at%20the%20Herald%20Square%20location%20in%20New%20York%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%