d%20interview%20with%20Brian%20Trautman%2C%20a%2047-year-old%20sailor%20and%20content%20creator%20who%20lives%20aboard%20a%20sailboat%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20daughter.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20working%20for%20Microsoft%20after%20graduating%20with%20an%20electrical-engineering%20degree%20in%202002.%20I%20quit%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvannevar.ece.uw.edu%2Fpeople%2Falumni%2Fprofiles%2Fbrian_trautman.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estart%20a%20software-development%20company%20with%20friends%20in%20Seattle%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20time%20I%20stumbled%20upon%20a%20book%20about%20how%20to%20cross%20an%20ocean%20in%20your%20own%20boat.%20That%20idea%2C%20though%20seemingly%20unattainable%2C%20stuck%20with%20me%20as%20an%20amazing%20thing%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sail%20boat%20with%20the%20sails%20down%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20blue%20sea.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ca8083ce697700198482eb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETrautman%20has%20sailed%20through%20the%20Caribbean%20on%20the%20boat%20where%20he%20married%20his%20wife.%3Cp%3EBrian%20Trautman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20morning%20in%20the%20late%202000s%20I%20was%20stuck%20in%20traffic%20on%20my%20commute%20when%20it%20hit%20me%20that%20my%20favorite%20part%20of%20the%20day%20was%20staring%20out%20of%20this%20bus%20window.%20It%20was%20the%20only%20time%20I%20wasn't%20consumed%20by%20the%20thoughts%20of%20customers%20and%20developers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20immediately%20knew%20I%20didn't%20want%20this%20life.%20I%20gave%20my%20business%20partners%20my%20year's%20notice%20in%202008%20and%20started%20selling%20everything%20to%20buy%20a%20sailboat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20had%20some%20experience%20sailing.%20I'd%20owned%20a%20small%20boat%20that%20I%20took%20out%20on%20a%20lake%20many%20afternoons%20%E2%80%94%20but%20that%20wasn't%20much%20to%20prepare%20me%20for%20crossing%20an%20ocean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EStarting%20my%20lifelong%20sailing%20adventure%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20SV%20Delos%2C%20a%2053-foot%20Amel%20Super%20Maramu%20sailboat%2C%20for%20%24390%2C000%20in%202008.%20I%20sold%20my%20house%20in%20Redmond%20to%20make%20a%20down%20payment%20and%20got%20a%20marine%20mortgage%20to%20cover%20the%20rest.%20The%20boat%20was%20eight%20years%20old%20at%20the%20time%2C%20so%20it%20was%20cheaper%20than%20buying%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20set%20off%20on%20my%20sailing%20adventure%20in%20August%202009%20with%20enough%20money%20to%20last%2018%20months.%20My%20initial%20plan%20was%20simply%20to%20make%20it%20to%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223928%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sailboat%20with%20a%20blue%20sail%20on%20the%20ocean.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ca807dce697700198482e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222946%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20SV%20Delos.%3Cp%3EBrian%20Trautman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20figured%20that%20by%20then%20I'd%20be%20mentally%20prepared%20to%20return%20to%20work%20in%20Seattle%2C%20sell%20my%20boat%2C%20and%20reenter%20my%20previous%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20by%20the%20time%20we%20landed%20in%20New%20Zealand%2C%20I'd%20fallen%20in%20love%20with%20sailing.%20When%20the%20initial%20money%20ran%20out%2C%20I%20took%20on%20engineering%20work%20on%20superyachts%20to%20refill%20the%20coffers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuckland%20is%20a%20big%20refit%20center%20for%20yachts%20based%20in%20the%20South%20Pacific%2C%20so%20it%20was%20a%20great%20place%20to%20make%20several%20hundred%20dollars%20a%20day%20working%20on%20engines%20and%20troubleshooting%20electrical%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20took%20on%20crew%20members%20who%20paid%20a%20share%20of%20our%20expenses%20to%20be%20part%20of%20our%20next%20sail%20to%20Fiji.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20months%20into%20my%20time%20in%20New%20Zealand%2C%20I%20met%20Karin%2C%20my%20future%20wife%2C%20who%20eventually%20joined%20me%20sailing%20full%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223124%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20diving%20off%20a%20sail%20boat%20into%20the%20ocean%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ca8078ce697700198482d6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222056%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKarin%2C%20Trautman's%20wife%2C%20diving%20off%20the%20sailboat.%3Cp%3EBrian%20Trautman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EWe%20work%20up%20to%204%20hours%20a%20day%20creating%20content%20to%20finance%20our%20travels%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20finance%20our%20travels%20by%20relying%20on%20crowdfunding%20and%20Patreon%20support%20and%20on%20our%20YouTube.%20We%20have%20832%2C000%20subscribers.%20We%20also%20sell%20SV%20Delos%20merch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20of%20the%20best%20times%20we've%20had%20on%20the%20boat%20were%20at%20the%20beginning%20when%20we%20had%20no%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20couldn't%20afford%20fuel%2C%20we%20had%20to%20sail%20everywhere%2C%20and%20that%20led%20to%20adventure.%20We've%20had%20times%20when%20we%20traded%20magazines%20for%20lettuce%20and%20tomatoes%2C%20and%20we%20learned%20to%20make%20our%20own%20beer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sailboat%20sailing%20on%20the%20water%20past%20rolling%20hills.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ca810ece697700198483f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221638%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETrautman%20has%20sailed%20to%2046%20countries%20on%20the%20Delos.%3Cp%3EBrian%20Trautman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20our%20days%20are%20spent%20creating%20content%20for%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40svdelos%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20we%20launched%20with%20regular%20content%20in%202012.%20The%20channel%20wasn't%20profitable%20until%202015.%20During%20that%20time%20we%20used%20savings%20to%20fund%20the%20journeys%20and%20keep%20us%20afloat%20financially%20while%20we%20filmed%20and%20edited%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20any%20given%20day%20it's%20a%20mix%20of%20filming%20and%20giving%20notes%20to%20video%20editors.%20I%20also%20do%20behind-the-scenes%20work%20like%20invoicing%20vendors%20and%20paying%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20exclude%20boat%20maintenance%2C%20I%20work%20three%20to%20four%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20as%20does%20Karin.%20We%20have%20plenty%20of%20time%20to%20spend%20afternoons%20enjoying%20the%20beach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224351%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20family%20sat%20on%20a%20sail%20boat%20typing%20on%20a%20laptop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ca807cce697700198482da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223263%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Trautmans%20working%20aboard%20their%20sailboat.%3Cp%3EBrian%20Trautman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20now%20have%20a%20remote%20team%20of%20seven%20employees%20who%20help%20produce%20videos.%20They%20also%20ship%20Delos%20merch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20does%20it%20cost%20to%20keep%20the%20boat%20running%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20paying%20%2410%2C000%20a%20year%20to%20insure%20the%20boat.%20Fuel%20costs%20vary%20widely%20from%20year%20to%20year%20depending%20on%20how%20far%20we%20travel.%20On%20average%2C%20fuel%20costs%20us%20%243%2C000%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20interior%20living%20area%20of%20a%20sailboat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ca8083ce697700198482f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223888%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20living%20area%20inside%20the%2053-foot%20sailboat.%3Cp%3EBrian%20Trautman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20monthly%20costs%20for%20food%20and%20living%20run%20about%20%243%2C500%20to%20%244%2C000.%20Generally%2C%20anchoring%20a%20boat%20is%20free.%20If%20there's%20a%20big%20storm%20coming%20that%20requires%20us%20to%20lift%20the%20boat%20out%20of%20the%20water%2C%20it'll%20cost%20%241%2C200%20to%20get%20it%20out%20and%20back%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20interior%20of%20a%20sailboat%20cabin.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ca8097ce69770019848320%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223888%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bedroom%20and%20storage.%3Cp%3EBrian%20Trautman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20kitchen%20inside%20the%20cabin%20of%20a%20sailboat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ca80a4ce69770019848338%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223888%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20boat's%20kitchen.%3Cp%3EBrian%20Trautman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20do%20have%20some%20luxuries%20on%20board%2C%20like%202%2C000%20watts%20of%20solar%20power%20and%20lithium%20batteries%2C%20a%20freezer%20that%20can%20store%20enough%20meat%20to%20last%20us%20four%20months%2C%20and%20stills%20to%20make%20our%20own%20moonshine.%20We%20make%20our%20own%20fresh%20water%20and%20take%20hot%20showers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223888%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20bathroom%20in%20a%20sailboat%20cabin.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ca808ace69770019848311%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bathroom%20on%20the%20boat.%3Cp%3EBrian%20Trautman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EStarting%20a%20family%20onboard%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigu