ion%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3ESailing%20the%20world%20has%20highs%20and%20lows%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20favorite%20memories%20on%20the%20boat%20was%20after%20we'd%20just%20sailed%203%2C000%20miles%20in%2019.5%20days%20from%20Mexico%20to%20the%20island%20of%20Fatu%20Hiva%2C%20part%20of%20French%20Polynesia.%20We%20were%20so%20excited%20just%20to%20be%20walking%20on%20dry%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20met%20a%20local%20who%20gifted%20us%20bananas%20and%20grapefruits.%20His%20generosity%20was%20so%20touching.%20We%20then%20went%20swimming%20under%20a%20waterfall%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20a%20perfect%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sailboat%20on%20the%20ocean.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ca809dce69770019848331%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20SV%20Delos%20at%20sail.%3Cp%3EBrian%20Trautman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESailing%20can%20also%20be%20dangerous.%20Our%20boat%20has%20been%20boarded%20illegally%20three%20times%20%E2%80%94%20in%20the%20Solomon%20Islands%2C%20western%20Papua%20New%20Guinea%2C%20and%20Madagascar%20%E2%80%94%20always%20around%203%20a.m.%20It's%20terrifying%20when%20this%20happens%2C%20but%20we%20scream%20bloody%20murder%20and%20the%20thieves%20flee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20happened%20in%202011%2C%20long%20before%20Sierra%20was%20born.%20Karin%20happened%20to%20be%20away%20at%20school.%20Before%20that%2C%20we%20never%20locked%20anything%20when%20we%20were%20off%20the%20boat%2C%20and%20we'd%20sleep%20with%20the%20doors%20open.%20We've%20since%20been%20more%20careful%2C%20including%20instituting%20night%20watches%20with%20a%20spotlight%20when%20sailing%20in%20areas%20where%20we%20felt%20uncomfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20keep%20machetes%20and%20fire%20extinguishers%20as%20weapons%20in%20the%20event%20of%20another%20emergency.%20But%20so%20far%2C%20having%20that%20spotlight%20to%20signal%20th