%3Cp%3ESimon%20Squibb%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EEntrepreneur%20Simon%20Squibb%20just%20spent%20%2432%2C000%20buying%20a%20stairwell%20in%20London.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20YouTuber%20was%20the%20winning%20bidder%20at%20an%20auction%20for%20the%20derelict%20stairwell%20this%20week.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESquibb%20says%20he%20plans%20to%20create%20office%20space%20to%20help%20people%20get%20new%20businesses%20up%20and%20running.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20city%20like%20London%20where%20an%20%26quot%3Bapartment%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.standard.co.uk%2Fhomesandproperty%2Fproperty-news%2Fmicro-studio-knightsbridge-no-toilet-b993063.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmaller%20than%20a%20parking%20space%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20no%20bathroom%20or%20kitchen%20was%20priced%20at%20about%20%24220%2C000%2C%20a%20property%20with%20a%20reserve%20price%20of%20just%20%C2%A320%2C000%20(%2425%2C000)%20might%20sound%20like%20an%20absolute%20bargain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20before%20getting%20too%20excited%20you%20might%20want%20to%20know%20that%20said%20%26quot%3Bproperty%26quot%3B%20in%20Twickenham%2C%20west%20London%2C%20is%20a%20disused%20staircase%20that%20no%20longer%20serves%20the%20office%20building%20it's%20attached%20to.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20listing%20caught%20the%20eye%20of%20Simon%20Squibb%2C%20an%20entrepreneur%20and%20YouTuber%2C%20who%20ended%20up%20paying%20%C2%A325%2C000%20(about%20%2432%2C000)%20to%20see%20off%20two%20other%20bidders.%20He%20hopes%20to%20use%20the%20space%20to%20help%20other%20budding%20entrepreneurs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7kOV5HRlOLA%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elisting%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20shared%20on%20YouTube%20shows%20an%20austere%20concrete%20stairwell%20surrounded%20by%20glass%2C%20with%20the%20interior%20littered%20with%20fire%20extinguishers%2C%20cardboard%20boxes%2C%20and%20even%20a%20grubby%20mattress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F7kOV5HRlOLA%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22200%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Disused%20stairwell%20for%20sale%20%20in%20London%20%20-%20Climbing%20the%20property%20ladder%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22113%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ESquibb%20heard%20about%20the%20property%20on%20a%20radio%20show%20just%20two%20days%20before%20Tuesday's%20auction%20and%20told%20Insider%20he%20had%20to%20act%20quickly%20to%20prepare%20a%20bid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20runs%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhelpbnk.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHelpBnk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20helps%20people%20start%20their%20own%20businesses%20with%20free%20advice.%20Squibb%20felt%20the%20steps%20were%20like%20how%20he%20views%20his%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20always%20talk%20about%20the%20elevator%20pitch%2C%20but%20an%20elevator's%20expensive%20%E2%80%93%20and%20it's%20much%20more%20fun%20to%20be%20in%20step%20by%20step.%20It's%20the%20first%20time%20in%20London%20there's%20steps%20for%20sale%2C%20and%20it%20jumped%20out%20at%20me%20as%20a%20good%20analogy%20for%20our%20first%20office%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESquibb%20plans%20to%20set%20up%20a%20HelpBnk%20office%20in%20the%20stairwell%20and%20offer%20space%20to%20budding%20entrepreneurs%20to%20help%20them%20get%20projects%20up%20and%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20seven%20landings%20within%20the%20stairwell%2C%20each%20of%20which%20Squibb%20hopes%20to%20convert%20into%20office%20space.%20He%20gets%20access%20to%20stairwell%20three%20weeks%20after%20the%20deal%20is%20finalized%20and%20then%20plans%20to%20call%20in%20contractors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20listing%20attracted%20media%20attention%20in%20the%20UK%20as%20another%20example%20of%20the%20out-of-control%20London%20property%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20can't%20do%20what%20they%20love%20because%20they've%20got%20huge%20rents%20to%20pay%20or%20huge%20mortgages%20to%20pay%2C%26quot%3B%20Squibb%20said.%20He%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-london-66369705%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20BBC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20became%20homeless%20as%20a%20teenager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESquibb%20says%20property%20developers%20suggested%20he%20could%20convert%20the%20stairwell%20into%20an%20apartment%20and%20make%2010%20times%20what%20he%20paid%20for%20the%20stairwell.%20It%20was%20an%20idea%20he%20rejected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BProperty%20can't%20be%20a%20business%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20real%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIn%20real%20businesses%20you%20create%20something%20that%20makes%20the%20world%20a%20better%20place%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20sure%20making%20the%20property%20market%20even%20more%20expensive%20is%20what%20I%20want.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20anyone%20thinking%20a%20large%20closet%20or%20a%20stairwell%20is%20the%20weirdest%20thing%20you%20can%20buy%20on%20the%20London%20property%20market%20%E2%80%93%20think%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20about%20%2463%2C000%20to%20spare%2C%20you%20could%20be%20the%20proud%20owner%20of%20an%20%26quot%3Bexciting'%26quot%3B%20121%20sq%20ft%20property%20in%20fashionable%20South%20Kensington%20that's%20%26quot%3Bonly%20a%2020-minute%20walk%20to%20Harrods.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20what's%20the%20catch%3F%20Well%2C%20it's%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rightmove.co.uk%2Fproperties%2F136832801%2