0Become%206.7-Trillion%20Economy%20By%202030%3A%20Rating%20Agency%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20grow%20at%20a%20rate%20of%206.7%20per%20cent%20per%20year%20from%202023-24%20and%20become%20a%20%246.7%20trillion%20economy%20by%202030-31%2C%20research%20and%20analytics%20firm%20Standard%20%26amp%3B%20Poor%20Global%20has%20said.%20India's%20Gross%20Domestic%20Product%20(GDP)%20was%20%243.4%20trillion%20in%202022-23.%20The%20rating%20agency%20also%20said%20that%20the%20per%20capital%20income%20in%20the%20country%20is%20projected%20to%20rise%20to%20about%20%244%2C500%20from%20%242%2C500.%20The%20report%20was%20released%20on%20a%20day%20when%20another%20agency%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-economy-boost-morgan-stanley-upgrades-india-status-to-overweight-downgrades-china-4264331%5C%22%3EMorgan%20Stanley%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20upgraded%20India%20to%20the%20'overweight'%20category%2C%20giving%20it%20top%20rating%20among%20emerging%20markets%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20India%20to%20grow%206.7%20per%20cent%20(average)%20from%20fiscal%202024%20to%20fiscal%202031%2C%20catapulting%20GDP%20to%20USD%206.7%20trillion%20from%20USD%203.4%20trillion%20in%20fiscal%202023.%20Per%20capital%20GDP%20will%20rise%20to%20about%20USD%204%2C500%2C%26quot%3B%20S%26amp%3BP%20Global%20said%20in%20a%20report%20titled%20'Look%20Forward%3A%20India's%20Money'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20agency%20warned%20that%20a%20global%20slowdown%20and%20lagged%20effect%20of%20a%20policy%20rate%20hike%20by%20RBI%20could%20slow%20down%20growth%20to%206%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20current%20fiscal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECapital%20accumulation%20will%20drive%20India's%20economy%20toward%20this%20desirable%20path%20with%20the%20government%20and%20increasingly%20private%20sector%20investing%20in%20infrastructure%20and%20manufacturing%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20will%20see%20growth%20peak%20at%20around%20fiscal%202025-26%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Crisil%20chief%20economist%20Dharmakirti%20Joshi%2C%20who%20was%20part%20of%20the%20team%20that%20prepared%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20said%20that%20India%20will%20likely%20see%20gains%20from%20reforms%20such%20as%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%20(GST).%20It%20added%20that%20implementation%20of%20the%20Insolvency%20and%20Bankruptcy%20Code%20would%20also%20help%20to%20drive%20a%20healthy%20credit%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%26amp%3BP%20Global%20said%20that%20even%20with%20India%20recalibrating%20toward%20manufacturing%2C%20services%20will%20maintain%20a%20strong%20role%20in%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20clocked%20a%207.2%20per%20cent%20GDP%20growth%20in%202022-23%20fiscal.%20Commerce%20and%20Industry%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20had%20called%20it%20%26quot%3Bhistoric%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20that%20India%20would%20emerge%20as%20a%20developed%20nation%20in%20the%20next%2025%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691133360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Fqse9bejg_india-economy-_625x300_03_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-to-grow-at-6-7-from-2024-become-6-7-trillion-economy-by-2030-rating-agency-4268243%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Standard%20%26amp%3B%20Poor%2C%20however%2C%20warned%20that%20a%20global%20slowdown%20and%20lagged%20effect%20of%20a%20policy%20rate%20hike%20by%20RBI%20could%20slow%20down%20growth%20to%206%25%20in%20the%20current%20fiscal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-to-grow-at-6-7-from-2024-become-6-7-trillion-economy-by-2030-rating-agency-4268243%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-to-grow-at-6-7-from-2024-become-6-7-trillion-economy-by-2030-rating-agency-4268243%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-to-grow-at-6-7-from-2024-become-6-7-trillion-economy-by-2030-rating-agency-4268243%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nuh%20Police%20Chief%2C%20on%20Leave%20When%20Communal%20Violence%20Began%2C%20Transferred%20to%20Bhiwani%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F02105512%2F8.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Days%20after%20communal%20clashes%20broke%20out%20in%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20Nuh%2C%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(SP)%20Varun%20Singla%2C%20who%20was%20on%20leave%20when%20the%20violence%20began%2C%20has%20been%20transferred%20to%20Bhiwani%20district%2C%20NDTV%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgurugram-violence-nuh-superintendent-of-police-varun-singla-transferred-after-communal-clashes-in-haryana-4267739%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingla%20has%20been%20replaced%20by%20IPS%20officer%20Narendra%20Bijarniya%20who%20has%20previously%20headed%20Nuh%E2%80%99s%20police%20force.%20Biijarniya%20was%20brought%20in%20as%20acting%20SP%20in%20Singla%E2%80%99s%20absence%20when%20the%20violence%20began%20during%20a%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHP)%20and%20Bajrang%20Dal%20rally%20on%20Monday%2C%20July%2031.%20Permanent%20orders%20have%20now%20been%20issued%20for%20his%20appointment%20as%20SP%20amid%20%E2%80%9Cintense%20communal%20tension%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20area%2C%20the%20NDTV%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20people%2C%20including%20two%20home%20guards%20and%20a%20cleric%2C%20died%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharyana-violence-mewat-hate-and-provocative-videos%5C%22%3Eclashes%20over%20an%20attempt%20to%20stop%20a%20VHP%20procession%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Unruly%20mobs%20set%20fire%20to%20several%20vehicles%2C%20food%20joints%2C%20and%20shops%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharyana-violence-mewat-hate-and-provocative-videos%5C%22%3EHaryana%20Violence%3A%20How%20Provocative%20Videos%20and%20a%20Background%20of%20Hate%20Preceded%20the%20Nuh%20Riots%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMewat%20is%20known%20for%20its%20composite%20culture%20and%20brotherhood.%20This%20violence%20has%20been%20instigated%20by%20some%20people%20through%20social%20media.%20A%20grand%20religious%20procession%20used%20to%20go%20through%20ancient%20temples%20here%2C%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20it%20has%20seen%20violence.%20Some%20troublemakers%20caused%20it%20through%20social%20media%20posts%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bijarniya%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20top%20Haryana%20government%20official%20on%20Thursday%2C%20August%203%20said%20anyone%20found%20responsible%20for%20the%20communal%20clashes%20will%20not%20be%20spared%20and%20claimed%20that%20the%20situation%20is%20fast%20returning%20to%20normal%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fchandigarh%2Fharyana-doles-out-numbers-93-firs-176-people-arrested-8875952%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Chief%20Secretary%20(Home)%20T.V.S.N.%20Prasad%20said%20a%20centre%20of%20the%20Rapid%20Action%20Force%20and%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%E2%80%99s%20(CRPF)%20anti-riot%20unit%20will%20soon%20be%20set%20up%20in%20Nuh%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20how%20the%20police%20were%20caught%20off-guard%20even%20when%20social%20media%20was%20rife%20with%20provocative%20videos%20about%20Bajrang%20Dal%20leader%20Monu%20Manesar%20coming%20to%20Nuh%20for%20the%20procession%2C%20Bijarniya%20said%20they%20had%20never%20imagined%20that%20such%20large-scale%20violence%20could%20happen%20in%20the%20area%2C%20the%20NDTV%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20monitoring%20social%20media%2C%20and%20the%20district%20police%20had%20made%20arrangements%20accordingly.%20We%20never%20imagined%20such%20large%20scale%20violence%20could%20happen.%20There%20have%20been%20shortcomings%2C%20no%20doubt%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20the%20violence%20happened.%20Top%20officials%20are%20investigating%20it%20now%20to%20ensure%20this%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20happen%20anywhere%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20according%20to%20their%20records%2C%20Manesar%20didn%E2%80%99t%20visit%20Nuh%2C%20and%20the%20violence%20started%20because%20of%20rumours%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManesar%20is%20wanted%20over%20his%20alleged%20role%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20two%20Muslim%20men%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Haryana%20government%20on%20Wednesday%20sought%20four%20more%20companies%20of%20central%20forces%20as%20arson%20and%20vandalism%20continued%20in%20Gurugram%20and%20a%20Bajrang%20Dal%20activist%20died%20in%20hospital%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Hindutva%20mob%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fi-was-scared-didnt-take-a-chance-muslim-workers-flee-after-violence-in-gurugrams-badshahpur%5C%22%3Evandalised%20shops%20and%20houses%20belonging%20to%20Muslim%20migrant%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Guruguram%E2%80%99s%20Badshahpur%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fi-was-scared-didnt-take-a-chance-muslim-workers-flee-after-violence-in-gurugrams-badshahpur%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20Was%20Scared%2C%20Didn%E2%80%99t%20Take%20a%20Chance%E2%80%99%3A%20Muslim%20Workers%20Flee%20After%20Violence%20in%20Gurugram%E2%80%99s%20Badshahpur%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20state%20police%2C%2020%20companies%20of%20central%20forces%20have%20been%20deployed%20in%20Haryana%20%E2%80%93%2014%20in%20Nuh%2C%20three%20in%20Palwal%2C%20two%20in%20Gurugram%20and%20one%20in%20Faridabad%2C%20the%20report%20said.%20Nearly%20176%20people%20have%20been%20arrested%20and%20over%2090%20detained%20in%20the%20state%20so%20far%20while%2041%20cases%20have%20been%20registered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%20government%20had%20suspended%20mobile%20internet%20and%20SMS%20services%20in%20Nuh%20on%20Monday%20and%20later%20imposed%20the%20restrictions%20in%20some%20other%20areas%20till%20August%202%20in%20view%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cintense%20communal%20tension%E2%80%9D%20and%20disturbance%20of%20public%20peace.%20The%20order%20was%20later%20extended%20till%20August%205.%20The%20internet%20will%20be%20temporarily%20restored%20today%20from%2012%20pm%20to%203%20pm%20in%20affected%20areas%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691133356000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F02105512%2F8.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fnuh-police-chief-on-leave-when-communal-violence-began-transferred-to-bhiwani%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Varun%20Singla%20has%20been%20replaced%20by%20Narendra%20Bijarniya%2C%20who%20has%20previously%20headed%20Nuh%E2%80%99s%20police%20force.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fnuh-police-chief-on-leave-when-communal-violence-began-transferred-to-bhiwani%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Experts%20Will%20Determine%20If%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%20Was%20Built%20On%20A%20Temple%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Archeological%20Survey%20of%20India%20(ASI)%20is%20conducting%20a%20scientific%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgyanvapi-mosque-survey-resumes-mosque-body-moves-supreme-court-4267669%5C%22%3Esurvey%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Varanasi%20which%20is%20located%20next%20to%20the%20iconic%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20temple.%20The%20survey%20was%20cleared%20by%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20over%20the%20petition%20by%20four%20women%20claiming%20that%20the%2017th-century%20mosque%20has%20been%20constructed%20over%20a%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20the%20survey%20being%20conducted%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindu%20activists%20claim%20that%20a%20temple%20existed%20earlier%20at%20the%20site%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgyanvapi-allahabad-high-court-yogi-adityanath-if-we-call-it-mosque-there-will-be-dispute-yogi-adityanath-on-gyanvapi-4254940%5C%22%3EGyanvapi%20mosque%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20was%20demolished%20in%20the%2017th%20century%20on%20the%20order%20of%20Mughal%20emperor%20Aurangzeb.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20was%20first%20ordered%20by%20a%20Varanasi%20district%20court%20after%20the%20petitioners%20claimed%20that%20a%20survey%20was%20the%20only%20way%20to%20determine%20if%20a%20temple%20had%20been%20razed%20to%20construct%20the%20landmark%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%225dakao58%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F5dakao58_gyanvapi-mosque-ani_625x300_04_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20ruling%2C%20the%20court%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20director%20of%20ASI%20is%20directed%20to%20conduct%20a%20detailed%20scientific%20investigation%20by%20using%20GPR%20survey%2C%20excavation%2C%20Dating%20method%20and%20other%20modern%20techniques%20of%20the%20present%20structure%20to%20find%20out%20as%20to%20whether%20same%20has%20been%20constructed%20over%20a%20pre-existing%20structure%20of%20Hindu%20temple.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20will%20the%20ASI%20determine%20if%20there%20was%20a%20temple%20at%20the%20site%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20team%20will%20conduct%20tests%20to%20determine%20the%20age%20of%20the%20pillars%20as%20well%20as%20the%20western%20wall%20of%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20radar%20survey%20will%20also%20be%20conducted%20to%20determine%20what%20lies%20below%20the%20structure%2C%20but%20it%20will%20be%20restricted%20to%20the%20three%20domes%20of%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%226tbusq7o%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-09%2F6tbusq7o_gyanvapi-mosque-650_625x300_13_September_22.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20team%20will%20also%20scan%20all%20the%20cellars%20in%20the%20compound%20and%20prepare%20a%20list%20of%20the%20artifacts%20that%20they%20find%20in%20the%20building.%20The%20artifacts%20found%20will%20also%20be%20tested%20to%20determine%20their%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20will%20be%20excluded%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20survey%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mosque's%20'wazukhana'%20-%20where%20a%20structure%20that%20the%20petitioners%20claimed%20was%20a%20'shivling'%20-%20will%20not%20be%20within%20the%20ambit%20of%20the%20survey%20in%20keeping%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20also%20directed%20the%20ASI%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20damage%20is%20caused%20to%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22rlrlma4%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Frlrlma4_gyanvapi-mosque-ani_625x300_04_August_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Director%20of%20ASI%20is%20also%20directed%20to%20ensure%20that%20there%20should%20be%20no%20damage%20to%20the%20structure%20standing%20on%20the%20disputed%20land%20and%20it%20remains%20intact%20and%20unharmed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691132580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fcm0r36u4_gyanvapi-ani_625x300_04_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgyanvapi-mosque-survey-explained-how-experts-will-determine-if-gyanvapi-mosque-was-