0some%20time%20now%2C%20we%20have%20been%20thinking%20of%20buying%20our%20own%20home%2C%20our%20%E2%80%9Cforever%E2%80%9D%20home%20where%20we%20would%20grow%20old%20together.%20We%20found%20one%20after%20much%20diligence.%20It%20was%20in%20a%20very%20tony%20part%20of%20South%20Delhi%3A%20wide%20roads%2C%20well-maintained%20parks%2C%20lush%20greenery%2C%20ample%20parking%2C%20in%20fact%20everything%20that%20comes%20together%20rather%20felicitously%20to%20make%20these%20neighbourhoods%20so%20scenic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20fly%20in%20the%20ointment%2C%20so%20to%20speak%2C%20was%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20mosque%20a%20few%20houses%20down%20the%20road%20%E2%80%93%20an%20old%20one%2C%20not%20especially%20architecturally%20significant%2C%20but%20one%20that%20has%20existed%20in%20that%20spot%20for%20a%20long%20time%20though%20clearly%20refurbished%20and%20modernised.%20Also%2C%20one%20that%20is%20evidently%20in%20use%20and%2C%20according%20to%20the%20estate%20agent%2C%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnuisance%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20but%20only%20on%20Fridays%2C%20he%20hastened%20to%20add%2C%20and%20also%20%E2%80%9Cthey%E2%80%9D%20don%E2%80%99t%20use%20any%20loudspeakers%20for%20%E2%80%9Ctheir%20%3Cem%3Eajaan%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%20However%2C%20to%20compound%20matters%2C%20every%20floor%20in%20that%20three-storey%20apartment%20block%20happened%20to%20be%20occupied%2Fowned%20by%20a%20Muslim%20family.%20After%20several%20visits%2C%20I%20eventually%20chickened%20out%20from%20buying%20that%20perfectly%20lovely%20apartment%20in%20a%20perfectly%20lovely%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20seemed%20to%20be%20a%20giant%2C%20invisible%20yet%20perfectly%20legible%20%E2%80%98X%E2%80%99%20marked%20on%20that%20building.%20The%20proximity%20to%20the%20mosque%2C%20and%20the%20presence%20of%20Muslim%20homeowners%20on%20every%20floor%20of%20that%20house%20in%20an%20otherwise%20entirely%20non-Muslim%20neighbourhood%2C%20brought%20visions%20of%20Ahmadabad%2C%20of%20the%20Gulbar