able%20weight%20and%20makes%20it%20difficult%20to%20breathe%20sometimes.%20I%20must%20also%20confess%20to%20an%20almost%20persistent%20depression%2C%20like%20a%20low-grade%20fever%2C%20over%20the%20past%20many%20months%2C%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20quite%20halt%20the%20daily%20rhythm%20of%20life%3B%20it%20just%20slows%20you%20down%20by%20its%20continuous%2C%20relentless%20presence%2C%20making%20you%20feel%20sad%20and%20empty%20and%20hopeless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20suspect%20I%20am%20not%20alone%20in%20this.%20I%20feel%20this%20fear%20and%20depression%20among%20a%20great%20many%20Muslims%20in%20urban%20India.%20I%20hear%20it%20in%20their%20silences.%20I%20sense%20it%20in%20their%20steadfast%20refusal%20to%20get%20drawn%20into%20political%20debates.%20I%20notice%20it%20in%20their%20stoicism%20in%20the%20face%20of%20virulent%20hate%20swirling%20about%20in%20school%20and%20college%20WhatsApp%20groups.%20I%20spot%20it%20in%20the%20hastily%20withdrawn%20social%20media%20posts%20drawing%20attention%20to%20some%20recent%20communal%20outrage%20or%20atrocity.%20I%20recognise%20it%20in%20their%20zeal%20to%20distance%20themselves%20from%20instances%20of%20%3Cem%3Eany%3C%2Fem%3E%20sort%20of%20violence%2C%20be%20it%20a%20Muslim%20man%20killing%20his%20Hindu%20girlfriend%20and%20chopping%20her%20into%20pieces%20or%20a%20Muslim%20man%20killing%20his%20non-Muslim%20partner%20in%20a%20business%20dispute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20my%20own%20fear%20and%20despair%2C%20and%20that%20of%20others%20like%20me%2C%20is%20so%20palpable%20and%20pronounced%2C%20what%20of%20those%20Muslims%20who%20are%20doubly%20marginalised%20by%20their%20poverty%20and%20illiteracy%3F%20Or%20vulnerable%20because%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20safeguards%20and%20barriers%2C%20however%20flimsy%2C%20that%20%E2%80%98people%20like%20us%E2%80%99%20have%20in%20our%20gated%20communities%20and%20cushioned%20lives%3F%20What%20of%20those%20who%20live%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20survival%20because%20they%20must%20perforce%20go%20out%20into%20the%20real%20world%20every%20single%20day%20to%20eke%20out%20a%20living%3F%20What%20of%20the%20plumbers%2C%20electricians%2C%20painters%2C%20carpenters%2C%20maids%20and%20sundry%20service%20providers%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20give%20their%20real%2C%20Muslim-sounding%20names%20for%20fear%20they%20will%20not%20be%20hired%3F%20Or%20the%20vegetable%20vendors%20who%20festoon%20their%20carts%20with%20saffron%20flags%20after%20every%20call%20to%20boycott%20small%20Muslim%20businesses%3F%20Or%20the%20biryani%20vendors%2C%20kebab%20sellers%2C%20quilt%20makers%2C%20car%20mechanics%20who%20have%20traditionally%20plied%20these%20trades%20for%20generations%20but%20now%20fear%20for%20their%20lives%3F%20What%20of%20the%20meat%20sellers%20whose%20makeshift%20stalls%20happen%20to%20be%20along%20the%20routes%20taken%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekawariyas%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20What%20of%20the%20imams%20and%20naib%20imams%2C%20often%20from%20the%20poorest%20of%20families%2C%20who%20are%20hired%20by%20Wakf%20boards%20to%20serve%20as%20custodians%20of%20small%2C%20isolated%20mosques%20surrounded%20by%20hostile%20neighbours%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%98look%E2%80%99%20like%20a%20Muslim%20so%2C%20to%20an%20extent%2C%20I%20am%20safe.%20Unless%20called%20out%20to%20chant%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shree%20Ram%E2%80%99%20to%20profess%20my%20Indianness%2C%20I%20am%20largely%20safe.%20But%20what%20of%20my%20name%3F%20How%20can%20I%20camouflage%20that%20on%20a%20railway%20booking%20chart%3F%20Or%20hide%20it%20when%20asked%20to%20provide%20proof%20of%20identity%3F%20While%20my%20first%20name%20can%20afford%20some%20benefit%20of%20doubt%20for%20it%20might%20pass%20as%20a%20Parsi%E2%80%99s%2C%20my%20surname%20is%20a%20dead%20give-away.%20When%20push%20comes%20to%20shove%20in%20the%20New%20India%20that%20is%20Bharat%2C%20not%20even%20speaking%20English%20will%20give%20me%20an%20exit%20pass%20if%20a%20mob%20baying%20for%20Muslim%20blood%20were%20to%20%3Cem%3Egherao%3C%2Fem%3E%20me.%20All%20my%20so-called%20privileges%20can%20be%20brought%20to%20naught%20by%20a%20lumpen%20crowd.%20The%20realisation%20is%20chilling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Muslim%20Life%20in%20India%20Has%20Become%20Dangerously%20Uncertain%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmuslim-life-in-india-has-become-dangerously-uncertain%5C%22%3EMuslim%20Life%20in%20India%20Has%20Become%20Dangerously%20Uncertain%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20I%20were%20a%20man%3F%20Imagine%2C%2070%20years%20after%20partition%20and%20after%20reading%20all%20the%20gory%20stories%20penned%20by%20Manto%20and%20other%20chroniclers%20of%20communal%20violence%2C%20having%20your%20pants%20pulled%20down%20to%20check%20whether%20you%20are%20a%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ekatua%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20or%20not%3F%20But%20what%20if%20I%20did%20%E2%80%98look%E2%80%99%20like%20a%20Muslim%3F%20What%20if%20I%20chose%20to%20offer%20%3Cem%3Enamaz%3C%2Fem%3E%20perfectly%20peacefully%20and%20quietly%20while%20sitting%20on%20my%20berth%20in%20a%20train%3F%20Worse%20still%2C%20what%20if%20I%20had%20a%20beard%2C%20wore%20a%20%3Cem%3Etopi%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20a%20%3Cem%3Ehijab%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20What%20if%20I%20worked%20as%20an%20imam%20in%20a%20mosque%3F%20So%20what%20if%20I%20had%20just%20assured%20my%20family%20that%20all%20was%20well%2C%20that%20I%20was%20safe%20given%20the%20police%20presence%20all%20around%20me%3F%20What%20then%3F%20What%20if%20I%2C%20as%20an%20Indian%2C%20have%20been%20conditioned%20to%20believe%20that%20the%20tattered%20fabric%20of%20secularism%20will%20be%20held%20up%20no%20matter%20what%3F%20The%20events%20of%20the%20past%20days%20prove%20these%20are%20no%20longer%20hypothetical%20scenarios.%20This%20is%20a%20lived%20reality%20for%20countless%20Indian%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EJab%20mulle%20kaate%20jaainge%2F%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3ERam%20Ram%20chillainge%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%20mein%20rehna%20hoga%2F%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EJai%20Shri%20Ram%20kehna%20hoga%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20even%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EGoli%20maro%20saalon%20ko%E2%80%A6%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0by%20someone%20who%20is%20now%20a%20Union%20minister%20are%20no%20longer%20isolated%20instances%20of%20random%2C%20unrelated%20personal%20biases%20and%20prejudices.%20These%20are%20dog%20whistles%2C%20a%20clarion%20call%20to%20a%20large%2C%20restive%20majority%20that%20is%20being%20brainwashed%20to%20believe%20they%20are%20second-class%20citizens%2C%20perhaps%20even%20lower%2C%20in%20their%20own%20land.%20All%20this%20is%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20narrative%2C%20a%20grand%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20we%20have%20clearly%20turned%20into%20a%20nation%20of%20%E2%80%98whatabouters%E2%80%99%2C%20each%20of%20these%20hate-filled%2C%20terror-inducing%20slogans%20will%20be%20instantly%20and%20viciously%20countered%20with%20those%20raised%20by%20the%20PFI%20or%20other%20fringe%20minority%20outfits.%20When%20rapes%2C%20murders%2C%20corruptions%2C%20scams%20and%20scandals%20are%20thwarted%20in%20Parliament%20by%20elected%20representatives%20of%20the%20people%20by%20instances%20of%20whatabouts%2C%20how%20can%20these%20rising%20incidents%20of%20bigotry%20and%20hate%20not%20be%20similarly%20countered%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20easier%20to%20come%20back%20with%20counter-accusations%2C%20to%20point%20fingers%2C%20to%20obfuscate%2C%20to%20fling%20more%20filth%2C%20to%20parry%20hate%20with%20hate%20than%20it%20is%20to%20understand%20fear%2C%20to%20acknowledge%20militant%2C%20muscular%20majoritarianism%2C%20to%20call%20out%20the%20elephant%20in%20the%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20spiral%20inexorably%20downwards%2C%20as%20every%20fresh%20instance%20of%20bigotry%20is%20outstripped%20and%20outdone%20by%20even%20bigger%2C%20bolder%2C%20more%20blatant%2C%20more%20bare-faced%20occurrences%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%