s%20guns%20and%20rifles%2C%20and%20several%20other%20arms%20and%20ammunition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20states%20that%20the%20mob%20broke%20open%20the%20doors.%20Though%20the%20police%20tried%20to%20avert%20the%20loot%20by%20firing%20327%20rounds%20of%20ammunition%20and%2020%20tear%20smoke%20shells%2C%20all%20of%20it%20was%20in%20vain%2C%20the%20FIR%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManipur%20has%20seen%20large%20scale%20loot%20of%20state%20armouries%20ever%20since%20the%20ethnic%20conflict%20began%20on%20May%203.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Farmoury-looted-policeman-killed-in-separate-incidents-in-manipur%2Farticle67155353.ece%2Famp%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20about%204%2C000%20weapons%20and%20lakhs%20of%20ammunition%20have%20been%20looted%20till%20now%2C%20of%20which%20only%201%2C600%20weapons%20have%20been%20recovered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-looted-weaponry-yet-to-return-to-police-armouries-cm-appeals-afresh-for-surrender%5C%22%3EManipur%3A%20FIRs%20Show%20the%20Type%20and%20Quantity%20of%20Weapons%20Taken%20from%20Police%20Armouries%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8BSeveral%20incidents%20of%20loot%20of%20weapons%20have%20taken%20place%20before.%20On%20several%20occasions%20state%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20and%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20state%20in%20May%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20have%20requested%20the%20people%20to%20return%20the%20weapons.%20One%20BJP%20MLA%20had%20even%20put%20up%20a%20drop%20box%20asking%20people%20to%20drop%20their%20weapons%20without%20fearing%20any%20reprisal%20from%20the%20state%20government.%20However%2C%20recovery%20remains%20very%20poor%20till%20date%2C%20and%20possession%20of%20such%20a%20huge%20cache%20of%20modern%20weapons%20remains%20an%20obstacle%20in%20normalcy%20returning%20to%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20was%20rocked%20by%20a%20fresh%20round%20of%20violence%20on%20August%203%20in%20the%20Bishnupur%20district%20as%20the%20Kuki%20community%20had%20planned%20a%20mass%20burial%20of%20people%20killed%20in%20the%20clashes.%20Though%20the%20burial%20was%20called%20off%2C%20the%20plan%20led%20to%20hundreds%20of%20Meitei%20women%20protesting%20close%20to%20the%20site%20where%20the%20burial%20was%20supposed%20to%20take%20place.%20To%20diffuse%20the%20situation%2C%20the%20RAF%20fired%20in%20the%20air%20with%20Manipur%20police%20keeping%20guard%20on%20the%20women%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIndiaToday%2Fstatus%2F1687028157063532544%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed.%20The%20video%20shows%20Manipur%20police%20firing%20at%20the%20RAF.%20Though%20after%20a%20brief%20exchange%20of%20fire%20from%20both%20the%20sides%2C%20it%20stopped.%20Several%20women%20were%20hurt%20in%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViolence%20also%20erupted%20in%20Imphal%20West%20on%20Thursday%2C%20and%20a%20police%20officer%20was%20killed%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-violence-manipur-attack-security-posts-ransacked-arms-and-ammunition-looted-in-manipur-4267688%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%3ENDTV%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20was%20shot%20in%20the%20head%20by%20a%20sniper.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691126841000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19203619%2FFyQ9vBxaIAAY1u3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-mob-loots-police-armoury-in-bishnupur-police-officer-killed-in-imphal-west%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20FIR%20states%20that%20the%20mob%20broke%20open%20the%20armoury%20doors.%20Though%20the%20police%20tried%20to%20avert%20the%20loot%20by%20firing%20327%20rounds%20of%20ammunition%20and%2020%20tear%20smoke%20shells%2C%20all%20of%20it%20was%20in%20vain%2C