dia.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20graduation%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F271536%2Fdesigners-use-renewable-solar-energy-rainwater-fashion%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Institute%20of%20Design%3C%2Fa%3E%20(NID)%2C%20Kirat%20started%20to%20work%20as%20an%20animation%20designer.%20%E2%80%9CI%20worked%20in%20the%20industry%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20for%20clients%20all%20over%20the%20country.%20I%20loved%20experimenting%20with%20design%20and%20various%20aspects%20of%20animation%2C%20but%20deep%20down%2C%20I%20always%20longed%20for%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2032-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Kirat%20lived%20in%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20he%20became%20more%20aware%20of%20the%20discrimination%20and%20lack%20of%20awareness%20concerning%20people%20from%20the%20Northeastern%20states.%20By%202020%2C%20when%20the%20pandemic%20hit%2C%20Kirat%20had%20made%20up%20his%20mind%20to%20return%20home%20and%20start%20looking%20for%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20product%20that%20highlights%20our%20culture%20to%20the%20upcoming%20generations.%20I%20also%20wanted%20to%20open%20a%20whole%20new%20world%20for%20people%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20Bodo%20culture.%20What%20could%20be%20a%20better%20way%20of%20introducing%20kids%20and%20people%20to%20my%20culture%20than%20with%20soft%20toys%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20he%20started%20Zankla%20Studio%20in%202021%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20showcasing%20the%20rich%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F135223%2Fassam-bodoland-lakme-women-weavers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20culture%20of%20the%20Bodo%20Tribe%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20studio%20creates%20handmade%20plastic-free%20soft%20toys%20that%20narrate%20stories%20deeply%20connected%20to%20the%20local%20culture%20and%20traditions%20of%20the%20Bodo%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERepresenting%20people%20from%20the%20Bodo%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-2-1-1690981872.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Each%20toy%20created%20at%20Zankla%20Studio%20carries%20a%20narrative%20native%20to%20the%20tribe%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-2-1-1690981872.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-2-1-1690981872-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-2-1-1690981872-500x261.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-2-1-1690981872-768x401.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fzankla-2-1-1690981872-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326113%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAll%20the%20toys%20that%20Kirat%20makes%20have%20a%20tribal%20folklore%20and%20story%20attached%20to%20them%3B%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Zankla%20Studio%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20growing%20up%2C%20I%20did%20not%20have%20toys%20that%20represented%20people%20like%20me%20and%20others%20from%20my%20community.%20The%20markets%20are%20flooded%20with%20Spiderman%2C%20Mickey%20Mouse%20and%20Barbie%20dolls.%20So%20I%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20to%20spread%20awareness%20among%20people%20about%20the%20existence%20of%20Northeastern%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20toy%20created%20at%20Zankla%20Studio%20carries%20a%20narrative%20native%20to%20the%20tribe%20or%20is%20a%20representation%20of%20a%20prominent%20person%20from%20the%20tribe%2C%20such%20as%20Ada%20Lowdoom%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Bodo%20traveller%2C%20Bodo%20Jwhwlao%20%E2%80%94%20a%20traditional%20Bodo%20fighter%2C%20Gowdang%20Rani%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Bodo%20princess.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20with%20a%20pamphlet%20containing%20the%20story%20or%20tale%20of%20the%20fictional%20or%20real%20character%20that%20the%20toy%20is%20based%20on%2C%20explains%20Kirat.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20sole%20purpose%20of%20these%20toys%20is%20to%20generate%20conversation%20among%20people%20about%20the%20community.%20A%20lot%20of%20research%20and%20thought%20is%20put%20into%20creating%20each%20toy.%20We%20have%20so%20many%20lost%20stories%20and%20characters%20from%20folklore.%20We%20create%20our%20toys%20based%20on%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FClQTdf4A6Sy%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FClQTdf4A6Sy%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%