0idea.%20I%20began%20thinking%20that%20this%20could%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmongst%20the%20people%20who%20tried%20the%20first%20trial%20batch%20was%20Renee%2C%20who%20absolutely%20loved%20the%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-3-1690980373.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dabbas%20are%20delivered%20on%20e-bikes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-3-1690980373.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-3-1690980373-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-3-1690980373-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-3-1690980373-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fdabba-3-1690980373-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-326062%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDabbas%20are%20delivered%20on%20e-bikes%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F283888%2Fdip-in-tiffin-dabba-by-srishti-garg-eco-friendly-packaging-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eidea%20of%20DabbaDrop%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20experienced%20it.%20I%20loved%20the%20theatre%20of%20not%20knowing%20what%20was%20inside%20the%20%3Cem%3Edabba%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebefore%20I%20opened%20it%2C%20and%20the%20wholesome%20food%20and%20sustainability%20element%20really%20ticked%20all%20the%20boxes%20for%20me%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Renee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20issues%20we%20face%20in%20the%2021st%20century%20is%20the%20problem%20of%20plenty.%20We%20simply%20have%20too%20much%20choice.%20Anshu%20wanted%20to%20combat%20that%20through%20her%20humble%20%3Cem%3Edabbas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20live%20in%20a%20world%20where%20we%20have%20to%20make%20so%20many%20choices%2C%20every%20single%20minute%20of%20the%20day.%20Our%20menus%20are%20set%20for%20the%20week.%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20choose.%20I%E2%80%99m%20making%20that%20one%20choice%20of%20what%20to%20have%20for%20dinner%20simpler%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Anshu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20wanted%20to%20introduce%20Londoners%20to%20Indian%20flavours%20and%20textures.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%20serve%20is%20not%20something%20that%20is%20easily%20available%20in%20a%20traditional%20Indian%20restaurant.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20Dabba%20Drop%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FtHhUYgJgp_U%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26rel%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D0%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26color%3Dred%26controls%3D1%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20can%20sign%20up%20weekly%20or%20fortnightly%2C%20and%20the%20menus%20are%20set%20for%20every%20week.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20get%20four%20freshly-cooked%20dishes%20%E2%80%94%20a%20salad%2C%20a%20%3Cem%3Esabzi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20%3Cem%3Edal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20curry%2C%20and%20rice.%20People%20can%20pause%20or%20skip%20their%20subscriptions.%20We%20are%20flexible.%20Our%20meals%20are%20vegan%20and%20South%20Asian.%20We%20want%20to%20follow%20the%20journey%20of%20the%20curry.%20This%20way%2C%20we%20are%20uncovering%20the%20history%20of%20Indians%20as%20they%20emigrated%20across%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20London%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20meals%20have%20to%20be%20pre-ordered.%20This%20way%2C%20the%20duo%20avoids%20wastage%20as%20the%20chefs%20know%20how%20many%20they%20are%20cooking%20for.%20One%20dabba%20can%20be%20enjoyed%20by%20two%20people%2C%20and%20they%20serve%20meals%20from%20Kerala%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20Vietnam%20and%20Japan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3Edabbas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20delivered%20on%20bicycles%2C%20e-bikes%20or%20other%20emission-free%20vehicles.%20A%20cloth%20is%20tied%20around%20the%20dabba%20which%20can%20be%20reused.%20The%20%3Cem%3Esamosas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Erotis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Enaans%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20tied%20in%20compostable%2C%20grease-proof%20paper%2C%20explains%20Anshu%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F64210%2Fjournalist-globetrotter-crowd-funds-money-dabbawallahs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eempty%20%3Cem%3Edabbas%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Eare%20picked%20up%20during%20the%20next%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20everything%20that%20is%20reusable.%20We%20are%20constantly%20trying%20to%20improve%20our%20packaging.%20We%20want%20to%20leave%20a%20better%20planet%20for%20our%20kids%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Anshu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20claim%20to%20have%20saved%202%2C03%2C370%20plastic%20containers%20and%20prevented%202%2C500%20kg%20of%20food%20waste%20through%20their%20venture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Anshu%20notes%20that%20her%20children%20were%20the%20biggest